Shared Types

Purpose: Cross-cutting type definitions, interfaces, records, and enumerations used by multiple modules or layers.

What belongs here:
- Shared interfaces (IAuthenticatable, ILogger, IConfigProvider, etc.)
- Common record types (TPaginationParams, TFilterCriteria, TSortOrder)
- Shared enumerated types (TUserRole, TLogLevel, THttpMethod, TCrudAction)
- Generic type aliases and type helpers
- API response envelope type definitions
- Cross-module DTOs that are not specific to one feature

Do NOT place here:
- Feature-specific DTOs (those belong in their module folder)
- Implementation classes (no services, repositories, or controllers)
- Any unit with database or WebBroker dependencies

